{
  "video_id": "HfFf1W5kVHY",
  "title": "Science-Backed Ways To Become A Better Leader",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 7100.0,
      "end_time": 10780.0,
      "text": "There are lots of myths in psychology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 10780.0,
      "end_time": 11850.0,
      "text": "things that people believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 11850.0,
      "end_time": 14183.0,
      "text": "there simply is no academic research for."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 15560.0,
      "end_time": 17100.0,
      "text": "When it comes to brainstorming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 17100.0,
      "end_time": 19350.0,
      "text": "right now around the world companies will all"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 19350.0,
      "end_time": 21650.0,
      "text": "be getting together to kick around some ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 21650.0,
      "end_time": 24159.0,
      "text": "and generate some new thoughts."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 24160.0,
      "end_time": 26200.0,
      "text": "A terrible, terrible idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 26200.0,
      "end_time": 28290.0,
      "text": "If you look at the research on brainstorming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 28290.0,
      "end_time": 31900.0,
      "text": "it decreases the number of ideas and the originality"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 31900.0,
      "end_time": 35100.0,
      "text": "of those ideas by around about 20%."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 35100.0,
      "end_time": 37140.0,
      "text": "Why? Because when we all get together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 37140.0,
      "end_time": 39660.0,
      "text": "the most dominant people take charge of the meeting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 39660.0,
      "end_time": 41779.0,
      "text": "and who knew they're not the most creative people"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 41780.0,
      "end_time": 43430.0,
      "text": "in the world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 43430.0,
      "end_time": 46490.0,
      "text": "A very, very simple change which is that you ask people"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 46490.0,
      "end_time": 49630.0,
      "text": "to brainstorm on their own to come up"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 49630.0,
      "end_time": 53330.0,
      "text": "with three innovative solutions before they get together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 53330.0,
      "end_time": 55550.0,
      "text": "and then when you get together you go around the group"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 55550.0,
      "end_time": 59370.0,
      "text": "and everyone talks about their solutions no matter how crazy"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 59370.0,
      "end_time": 62910.0,
      "text": "actually increases innovation and creativity."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 62910.0,
      "end_time": 64479.0,
      "text": "Again, a very, very simple change."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 64480.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66783.0,
      "text": "A very easy change, but a very powerful one."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68740.0,
      "end_time": 70900.0,
      "text": "When it comes to meetings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 70100.0,
      "end_time": 72440.0,
      "text": "often we all like to sit around and we all like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 72440.0,
      "end_time": 75300.0,
      "text": "quite frankly, to waste a great deal of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 75300.0,
      "end_time": 77850.0,
      "text": "If you stand up in a meeting, a standing meeting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 77850.0,
      "end_time": 79470.0,
      "text": "it doesn't reduce productivity."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 79470.0,
      "end_time": 82160.0,
      "text": "What it does do is massively reduce the time of the meeting."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 82160.0,
      "end_time": 84170.0,
      "text": "People want to be out of that room quickly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 84170.0,
      "end_time": 87623.0,
      "text": "so they're just as productive in a much, much shorter time."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 90300.0,
      "end_time": 92520.0,
      "text": "Also, if you think that a colleague"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 92520.0,
      "end_time": 96170.0,
      "text": "or maybe a client is not being entirely straight with you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 96170.0,
      "end_time": 97690.0,
      "text": "what's the best thing to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 97690.0,
      "end_time": 100399.0,
      "text": "to try and find out if they're being economical"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 100400.0,
      "end_time": 101690.0,
      "text": "with the truth?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 101690.0,
      "end_time": 102810.0,
      "text": "Well, if you look at the amount"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 102810.0,
      "end_time": 105920.0,
      "text": "of lying across different types of communication,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 105920.0,
      "end_time": 108980.0,
      "text": "you see people lie a lot face-to-face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 108980.0,
      "end_time": 112260.0,
      "text": "a bit less on the phone, a little bit in texting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 112260.0,
      "end_time": 114410.0,
      "text": "but absolutely not in emails."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 114410.0,
      "end_time": 117740.0,
      "text": "Only around about 10% of emails carry a lie,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 117740.0,
      "end_time": 121520.0,
      "text": "because people don't want to commit themselves to print."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 121520.0,
      "end_time": 123899.0,
      "text": "And so If you think someone isn't being entirely straight with you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 123900.0,
      "end_time": 126170.0,
      "text": "just say, \"Oh, can you email me about that?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 126170.0,
      "end_time": 127270.0,
      "text": "and instantly you'll find out whether"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 127270.0,
      "end_time": 129502.0,
      "text": "or not they're being economical with the truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 130889.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131724.0,
      "text": "At the moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 131724.0,
      "end_time": 134140.0,
      "text": "we're trying to cut down on sleep as much as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 134140.0,
      "end_time": 136529.0,
      "text": "There's an epidemic of sleeplessness"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 136530.0,
      "end_time": 138830.0,
      "text": "and sleep is absolutely vital."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 138830.0,
      "end_time": 141960.0,
      "text": "It underpins productivity, it underpins focus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 141960.0,
      "end_time": 144300.0,
      "text": "it underpins creativity."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 144300.0,
      "end_time": 145510.0,
      "text": "What's happening right at the moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 145510.0,
      "end_time": 147980.0,
      "text": "is we're taking our smartphones to bed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 147980.0,
      "end_time": 149959.0,
      "text": "often putting them on our bedside table"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 149960.0,
      "end_time": 152300.0,
      "text": "and treating them as alarm clocks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 152300.0,
      "end_time": 153670.0,
      "text": "and then, of course, in the middle of the night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 153670.0,
      "end_time": 156589.0,
      "text": "you wake up, I think I'll just check social media"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 156590.0,
      "end_time": 159990.0,
      "text": "or whatever it is and you get this blast of light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 159990.0,
      "end_time": 161870.0,
      "text": "which actually contains blue light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 161870.0,
      "end_time": 164380.0,
      "text": "which is very disruptive to the production of melatonin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 164380.0,
      "end_time": 167600.0,
      "text": "which is essential to sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 167600.0,
      "end_time": 170150.0,
      "text": "And then it really messes up the rest of the night."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 170150.0,
      "end_time": 172300.0,
      "text": "So, value sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 172300.0,
      "end_time": 175500.0,
      "text": "If there's any way of incorporating a 20-minute nap"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 175500.0,
      "end_time": 177960.0,
      "text": "into the middle of the day, really good for productivity."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 177960.0,
      "end_time": 179920.0,
      "text": "Businesses should be doing that."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 179920.0,
      "end_time": 183623.0,
      "text": "Value sleep."
    }
  ]
}